Summary:        The Python SQL Toolkit and Object Relational Mapper
Name:           python-sqlalchemy
Version:        1.0.15
Release:        2%{?dist}
Url:            http://www.sqlalchemy.org
License:        MIT
Group:          Development/Languages/Python
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
